Media
Manga
Written and illustrated by , Gold Kingdom and Water Kingdom was serialized in Shogakukan's  manga magazine Flowers from October 28, 2014, to April 28, 2016. The series was collected into a single  volume, published by Shogakukan on July 8, 2016.
In March 2023, Seven Seas Entertainment announced that it licensed the series for English publication. The volume was released on November 28 of the same year.
